description: Meat the Greek is brought to you by the talented and passionated The Mavropoulos family. After moving here from Greece, they’re taking their very own age-old recipes through LA and giving everyone a delightfully authentic taste of gourmet Greek cuisine. A few of their tasty specialties include delicious grilled skewers with your choice of meat, hot pita wraps, and fresh cut salads bursting with veggies. For all this and more, you simply must introduce yourself to the amazing meals from Meat the Greek!
name: Meat the Greek
